segmentosSRT.text: Careful, slowly. Don't move too fast!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
Your mother's not well.
Go now, for her sake.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: I'll look after her for a few days?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: I've given up the puppet troupe.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
I don't gamble anymore.
Don't want to end up like you.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: This case is in the way!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Whose is it? Get rid of it!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
Sir, it's mine.
I've got my things in it. Let me keep it.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Get it out of my sight then.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
It's just a bunch of puppets.
Get rid of them! This is war!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
- Where'd you get them?
- Off the corpses.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
- Are you going or not?
- No!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text:
- I'm telling you to go!
- No!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Youqing's not going to any stupid show.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: and blinds all who look within
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: I yell there's no time to waste
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13

segmentosSRT.text: Far away, we flee with haste
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_13
